---
title: Sweet Potato and Poblano Quesadillas with Southwest Crema and Radish Tomato Salad
description: As we’ve grown more sophisticated in this life, so have our quesadillas. Gone are the days of the microwaved renditions of our youth (they got the job done, but they definitely weren’t delicious). This *cosmopolitan quesadilla* is jam-packed with flavorful roasted veggies and tons of gooey, melty cheese. On top, there’s a crunchy radish salsa and dollops of spiced lime crema. A good thing just got a whole lot better.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w19-r8-sweet-potato-and-poblano-quesadillas-9cbe0b92.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-potato-and-poblano-quesadillas-5c9bb0cde3f3394f9d2c7e22-eee0b3f4.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-potato-and-poblano-quesadillas-5c9bb0cde3f3394f9d2c7e22
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 710 kcal
  fat: 41 g
